    <div class="hero-text">
      <hgroup>
        <h1>About</h1>
        <p>
          WaveFEM began as a hobby to understand electromagnetic simulation. We
          wrote the core simulation kernel from scratch, making it highly
          performant and easy to extend. Without the high overhead of a large
          company, we can offer this powerful software at a fraction of the
          cost, making it ideal for students, researchers, and engineers.
        </p>
      </hgroup>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-image">
      {% image "/assets/Hero Magic T Sim.webp", "Hero Magic T Sim", "hero-img" %}
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<section>
  <div class="container" data-theme="light">
    <h2>Core Features</h2>
    <p>
      The core simulation code is finished and includes comprehensive
      electromagnetic simulation capabilities designed for accuracy and
      performance.
    </p>

    <div class="grid">
      <article>
        <h4>3D Field Solver</h4>
        <div>
          <p>
            Integrated meshing and adaptive mesh refinement for optimal accuracy
            and computational efficiency across complex geometries.
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article>
        <h4>Radiation Boundaries</h4>
        <div>
          <p>
            Perfectly Matched Layers (PMLs) provide accurate absorption of
            outgoing waves for open-region electromagnetic problems.
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>

    <div class="grid">
      <article>
        <h4>Far-Field Computation</h4>
        <div>
          <p>
            Integrated near-to-far-field transformation enables accurate antenna
            pattern and RCS calculations from near-field data.
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article>
        <h4>Fast Vector Fitting</h4>
        <div>
          <p>
            Advanced interpolation techniques for efficient frequency sweeps,
            reducing simulation time while maintaining accuracy.
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="container" data-theme="light">
    <h2>Import & Design Tools</h2>
    <p>
      Seamless integration with industry-standard CAD formats and powerful
      parametric design capabilities for rapid prototyping and optimization.
    </p>

    <div class="grid">
      <article>
        <h4>Multi-Format Support</h4>
        <div>
          <p>
            Import multi-object .step files, planar formats like .gds and .dxf,
            with a built-in substrate editor for complete design flexibility.
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article>
        <h4>Port Configuration</h4>
        <div>
          <p>
            Comprehensive lumped and wave port support with integrated 2D
            eigensolver for both TEM and TE mode analysis.
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>

    <div class="grid">
      <article>
        <h4>Material Assignment GUI</h4>
        <div>
          <p>
            Intuitive graphical interface for material and port assignment,
            streamlining the simulation setup process.
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article>
        <h4>Parametric Modeling</h4>
        <div>
          <p>
            Create sophisticated parametric models using CadQuery scripts for
            design optimization and sensitivity analysis.
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
